casebody.data:
ROONEY v. STANDARD ROOFING & MATERIAL CO. No. 11303 Opinion Filed May 29, 1923.

Commissioners’ Opinion,

Division No. 2. Neff & Neff, for plaintiff in error. Wm. A. Killey and S. H. Lattimore, for defendants in error.

Opinion by

JARMAN, C.

The petition in error and case-made were filed in this court April 2, 1920. The plaintiff in error has failed to file brief as required by rule 7 of this court (47 Okla. vi). For failure to comply with this rule this appeal is dismissed for want of prosecution.

By the Court: It is so ordered.
